{"tha-ap531:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap531:0.2":"Tinadayakavagga ","tha-ap531:0.3":"Amandaphaladayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap531:1.1":"“Padumuttaro nama jino, ","tha-ap531:1.2":"sabbadhammana paragu; ","tha-ap531:1.3":"Vutthahitva samadhimha, ","tha-ap531:1.4":"cankami lokanayako. ","tha-ap531:2.1":"Kharibharam gahetvana, ","tha-ap531:2.2":"aharanto phalam tada; ","tha-ap531:2.3":"Addasam virajam buddham, ","tha-ap531:2.4":"cankamantam mahamunim. ","tha-ap531:3.1":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap531:3.2":"sire katvana anjalim; ","tha-ap531:3.3":"Sambuddham abhivadetva, ","tha-ap531:3.4":"amandamadadim phalam. ","tha-ap531:4.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap531:4.2":"yam phalam adadim tada; ","tha-ap531:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap531:4.4":"amandassa idam phalam. ","tha-ap531:5.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap531:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap531:5.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap531:6.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap531:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap531:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap531:7.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap531:7.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap531:7.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap531:8.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma amandaphaladayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap531:9.1":"Amandaphaladayakattherassapadanam navamam. "}